# Styling Tables üé®

Tables look ugly by default. CSS makes them shine.

## Borders
```css
table, th, td {
  border: 1px solid black;
  border-collapse: collapse;
}
```

## Padding & Spacing
```css
th, td {
  padding: 15px;
}
```

## Zebra Stripes
```css
tr:nth-child(even) {
  background-color: #f2f2f2;
}
```
